    <h2>Message Frequency</h2>
    <p>Message frequency varies based on your account activity and service notifications. You may receive up to several messages per month.</p>

    <h2>Message &amp; Data Rates</h2>
    <p>Message and data rates may apply. Please contact your mobile carrier for details about your plan.</p>

    <h2>Opt-Out</h2>
    <p>To stop receiving SMS messages from Engage Communications at any time, reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. You will receive a confirmation and no further messages will be sent.</p>

